    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = ((wp.sin(v0 + 0.73) / (v2 + 0.65 + v0 + 0.69)) + wp.exp(0.48))
    v2 = 0.27
    v2 = (((v1 + 0.48 / v0 + 0.34) * (tmp + 0.07 - v2 + 0.79)) - 0.77)
    v0 = (tmp - (wp.sin(v0 + 0.44) / (v2 + 0.21 * v0 + 0.69)))
    v2 = (wp.cos(wp.exp(v2 + 0.74)) / wp.exp((v0 + 0.23 * v1 + 0.58)))
    v0 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
